%F A008287 From _Vladimir Shevelev_, Dec 15 2010: (Start)
%F A008287 T(n,0) = 1; T(n,3*n) = 1; T(n,k) = T(n,3*n-k);
%F A008287 T(n,k) = 0, iff k<0 or k>3*n; Sum{k=0..3*n} T(n,k) = 4^n; Sum{k=0..3*n}((-1)^k)*T(n,k)=0 for n > 0; [corrected by _Werner Schulte_, Sep 09 2015]
%F A008287 T(n,k) = Sum{i=0..floor(k/2)} C(n,i)*C(n,k-2*i);
%F A008287 T(n+1,k) = T(n,k-3)+T(n,k-2)+T(n,k-1)+T(n,k). (End)
%F A008287 T(n,k) = Sum_{i = 0..floor(k/4)} (-1)^i*C(n,i)*C(n+k-1-4*i,n-1) for n >= 0 and 0 <= k <= 3*n. - _Peter Bala_, Sep 07 2013
%F A008287 G.f.: 1/(1 - ( x + y*x + y^2*x +y^3*x )). - _Geoffrey Critzer_, Feb 05 2014
%F A008287 T(n,k) = Sum_{j=0..k} (-2)^j*binomial(n,j)*binomial(3*n-2*j,k-j) for n >= 0 and 0 <= k <= 3*n (conjectured). - _Werner Schulte_, Sep 09 2015
